OL,3,CUndercover police inquiry to hear
OL,4,Cjustice campaigners' 'deeply moving'
OL,5,Cevidence
OL,7,FRace issues will be "particularly
OL,8,Fprominent" in the latest stage of a
OL,9,Fmammoth public inquiry into undercover
OL,10,Fpolicing, a hearing has been told,
OL,11,Fwith "deeply moving, at times
OL,12,Fharrowing" evidence from those who
OL,13,Fwere spied upon.
OL,15,FThe latest stage of the Undercover
OL,16,FPolicing Inquiry began on Monday,
OL,17,Fexamining the activity of the shadowy
OL,18,FMetropolitan Police Special
OL,19,FDemonstration Squad (SDS) between 1993
OL,20,Fand 2007.
