OL,5,Cevidence
OL,7,FMaking his opening statement, counsel
OL,8,Fto the inquiry David Barr KC said:
OL,9,F"The issue of race will be
OL,10,Fparticularly prominent. There is a
OL,11,Fgreat deal of SDS reporting on a large
OL,12,Fnumber of racial justice campaigns
OL,13,Fduring this era."
OL,15,FHe said the inquiry will hear from
OL,16,Fcampaigners including the parents of
OL,17,Fmurdered Stephen Lawrence, and Sukhdev
OL,18,FReel, whose son Ricky died in what she
OL,19,Fbelieves was a racist attack.
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@QO]
