OL,4,Cjustice campaigners' 'deeply moving'
OL,5,Cevidence
OL,7,F"The traumas experienced by each of
OL,8,Fthese people are clearly set out in
OL,9,Ftheir deeply moving, at times,
OL,10,Fharrowing evidence," Mr Barr said.
OL,12,FThe inquiry will look at whether there
OL,13,Fwas "conscious or subconscious racism"
OL,14,Fin the deployments of SDS undercover
OL,15,Fofficers.
OL,17,FOther campaigns that were targeted in
OL,18,Fthe same period included environmental
OL,19,Fgroups, anti-war campaigners, and
OL,20,Fanimal rights activists.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@TO]uD@EOUuD@fO]
