OL,5,Cevidence
OL,7,FIt also saw "a seismic change" brought
OL,8,Fabout by the 9/11 attacks in the US in
OL,9,F2001, Mr Barr said, the July 7 attacks
OL,10,Fin London four years later, and the
OL,11,Fmistaken shooting of innocent
OL,12,FBrazilian Jean Charles de Menezes at
OL,13,FStockwell Tube station.
OL,15,FThe inquiry will look at how and why
OL,16,Fthe SDS reported on his family's
OL,17,Fjustice campaign.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@^O]
