OL,4,Cjustice campaigners' 'deeply moving'
OL,5,Cevidence
OL,7,FOn Friday, the father of Stephen
OL,8,FLawrence, Neville Lawrence, welcomed
OL,9,Fthe chance for evidence to be heard in
OL,10,Fpublic about how the battle for
OL,11,Fjustice for his son was spied upon.
OL,13,FHe said the surveillance by police
OL,14,Fmoles who posed as anti-racism
OL,15,Fcampaigners in the late 1990s was
OL,16,F"bewildering and insulting".
OL,18,FThe public inquiry was announced by
OL,19,Fthen-home secretary Theresa May in
OL,20,F2015, after former SDS officer Peter
OL,21,FFrancis turned whistleblower.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@[O]
