OL,5,Cevidence
OL,7,FHe told The Guardian newspaper that he
OL,8,Fhad been tasked with gathering
OL,9,Finformation to smear the Lawrence
OL,10,Ffamily, something the Met has always
OL,11,Fdenied.
OL,13,FIt has already emerged that one
OL,14,Fundercover officer who used the fake
OL,15,Fname David Hagan, as well as Mr
OL,16,FFrancis, joined the Movement for
OL,17,FJustice in the late 1990s and remained
OL,18,Fa member for two or three years.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
