OL,4,Cjustice campaigners' 'deeply moving'
OL,5,Cevidence
OL,7,FThis was during the Macpherson public
OL,8,Finquiry into both Stephen's murder and
OL,9,Fthe alleged corruption, racism and
OL,10,Fincompetence that dogged the police
OL,11,Finvestigation into his death.
OL,13,FMr Francis attended the inquiry
OL,14,Fpretending to be a supporter of the
OL,15,FLawrence campaign, while feeding
OL,16,Finformation back to colleagues in the
OL,17,FMet.
OL,19,FHe is due to give evidence to the
OL,20,Finquiry in December.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
