OL,3,CUndercover police inquiry to hear
OL,4,Cjustice campaigners' 'deeply moving'
OL,5,Cevidence
OL,7,FThe inquiry will examine the
OL,8,Factivities of Mr Francis, David Hagan
OL,9,Fand four other undercover officers in
OL,10,Fthe next three months.
OL,12,FMr Hagan, also referred to as HN81,
OL,13,Fadmitted being involved in scuffles
OL,14,Foutside the Macpherson Inquiry when
OL,15,Fthe five prime suspects attended,
OL,16,Fcausing Neville and Doreen Lawrence to
OL,17,Fmake public appeals for calm.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
