OL,3,CUndercover police inquiry to hear
OL,4,Cjustice campaigners' 'deeply moving'
OL,5,Cevidence
OL,7,FNeville Lawrence told the inquiry it
OL,8,Fis "particularly troubling that an
OL,9,Fofficer who sought to justify
OL,10,Fsurveillance on the grounds of public
OL,11,Fdisorder actively contributed to it".
OL,13,FPeter Skelton KC, representing the
OL,14,FMetropolitan Police Commissioner, said
OL,15,Fin his opening statement that the
OL,16,Fforce apologises to the family of
OL,17,FStephen Lawrence, his friend Duwayne
OL,18,FBrooks, Sukhdev Reel, and other
OL,19,Fjustice campaigners for the monitoring
OL,20,Fthat affected them.
OL,26,@pD@DOUsD@dO]
