OL,3,CUndercover police inquiry to hear
OL,4,Cjustice campaigners' 'deeply moving'
OL,5,Cevidence
OL,7,F"This is reflective of an 'us against
OL,8,Fthem' culture that prevailed within
OL,9,Fthe MPS at that time, which didn't
OL,10,Fproperly distinguish between
OL,11,Flegitimate intelligence targets, such
OL,12,Fas groups committed to inciting
OL,13,Fserious public disorder, and
OL,14,Fillegitimate targets such as grieving
OL,15,Fblack and Asian families who were
OL,16,Fcomplaining about injustice and the
OL,17,Factions of the police."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@WO]
