OL,5,Cevidence
OL,7,FHe said the sexual relationships were
OL,8,F"a gross violation of privacy and
OL,9,Fhuman rights", and that SDS managers
OL,10,Fhad "failed to recognise the hurt,
OL,11,Fdistress and anger" that would be
OL,12,Fcaused to bereaved families through
OL,13,Fthe use of the identities.
